data.content: Obdurate is a formal word meaning stubborn. If you want to major in English, but your parents are obdurate that you should go premed, they might go so far as to threaten not to pay your tuition.

data.content: To grovel is to beg like a hungry dog. You don't have to be a canine, though, you might grovel for a better grade (please don't).

not responding to treatment
